{"tid":1696460,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"用信用卡俾隧道費","createTime":"2019-11-06T07:31:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T02:42:12.000Z","uid":66242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0d848456f7ec4dde1b674741728cf3a41b17c456","tid":1696460,"uid":66242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T07:31:39.000Z","msg":"之前用開八達通<br />\n近排用匯豐卡過唔到隧道<br />\n紅燈加橫線<br />\n即係失敗<br />\n係咪好似記得唔知邊度有人講過<br />\n用信用卡俾隧道錢<br />\n每十次就要喺商舖簽一次 online transaction?<br />\n即係隧道收信用卡其實係 offline?<br />\n但如果是咁<br />\n點解又唔收 citibank 信用卡？<br />\nCitibank：<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n10. 為甚麼我未能於隧道使用Visa payWave付款?   由於「停車拍卡」式電子繳費設施未能支援本行Visa payWave信用卡之設定，故客戶暫時未能使用本行Visa payWave信用卡於隧道付款。請放心，你仍然可於其他商戶使用Visa payWave付款。     11. 為甚麼其他銀行的payWave 信用卡可以支援於隧道付款?   不同銀行信用卡所提供的Visa payWave 都有不同的設定，Citi 信用卡所提供的Visa payWave功能只支援在線授權交易，但「停車拍卡」式電子繳費設施暫時未能支援本行Visa payWave卡之設定。我們亦已經就此向運輸署反映。     12. 甚麼時候會支援隧道付款?   請留意運輸署的最新通告。<br />\n</blockquote>"},{"pid":"bcc5f81c8e6910a1791ee4c6b8aad1b5bfbade07","tid":1696460,"uid":256999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T03:41:25.000Z","msg":"每日都係信用咭過隧道, 無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deb65dc6ed06d021ae81b56afa53044d5bf15854","tid":1696460,"uid":61250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T02:30:21.000Z","msg":"貼到痴撚住部機就得<br />\n利申：實測好多次"},{"pid":"5dc6c45ab1e379d74a0be276607a439d48aeac75","tid":1696460,"uid":10593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T02:40:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ea913a3dbd1cf2424f7378fcf5fcdc2c6e9a940","tid":1696460,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T02:40:50.000Z","msg":"***眾籌***<br />\n唔好意思，仲係要借個位&amp;幫你推推POST<br />\n<br />\n鐘庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港性民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意 (eg. 721, 831) &amp; 證明香港人未放棄，然後做份國際文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 話比全世界聽：5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n(<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌到而家先58%</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 仲要大家支持)<br />\n<br />\n第三&amp;四期民調結果POST <span style=\"color: red;\">(new)</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1</a><br />\n第二期民調結果POST <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054</a><br />\n第一期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n<br />\n眾籌link:  <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=5WD1fpiCBK613UyTU9OnX%2FTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=c4e5d0d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a><br />\n官方link (我們香港人計劃) :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2F&d=5WD1fpiCBK613UyTU9OnX%2FTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=8af10544\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n(對唔住，我知而家仲叫大家課金可能好反感，但我相信兄弟爬山，各有各做)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a923ed9ae46d220185dec39f597f34529b6d4090","tid":1696460,"uid":10901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T02:42:12.000Z","msg":"邊張？<br />\n次次都唔得既"}]}